{"tid":2242123,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"LLY人造抗體臨床第三試驗出現安全問題，需要緊急停止試驗。","createTime":"2020-10-13T19:12:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-15T09:05:48.000Z","uid":38861,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"86b7cb40ccfdeaab3934d2b352fa791674133de3","tid":2242123,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T19:12:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/live/2020/10/13/world/coronavirus-covid/eli-lilly-antibody-trial-is-paused-because-of-potential-safety-concerns\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Flive%2F2020%2F10%2F13%2Fworld%2Fcoronavirus-covid%2Feli-lilly-antibody-trial-is-paused-because-of-potential-safety-concerns&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2ptjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=3b8ebcb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/live/2020/10/13/world/coronavirus-covid/eli-lilly-antibody-trial-is-paused-because-of-potential-safety-concerns</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時步入臨床第三試驗的人造抗體分別有LLY及REGN兩間，LLY現時因安全問題要停止試驗，而REGN九月尾已初步公開透露第三試驗正面結果，並在9月14日已參加英國為期28日的RECOVERY TRIAL第三試驗，相信將會在本星期或下星期發表結果。<br />\n<br />\n雖然REGN大有機會成為武肺治療及預務兼備一身的救星，但人造抗體成本昂貴，而且公司透露暫時最大產量為30K左右，不足以應付實際市場。<br />\n<br />\n究竟同樣有參與人造抗體研發的SRNE值唔值得買呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b5a6ae92d4cc747267aa6befcc551ae1769ddf","tid":2242123,"uid":343574,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"86b7cb40ccfdeaab3934d2b352fa791674133de3","tid":2242123,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T19:12:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/live/2020/10/13/world/coronavirus-covid/eli-lilly-antibody-trial-is-paused-because-of-potential-safety-concerns\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Flive%2F2020%2F10%2F13%2Fworld%2Fcoronavirus-covid%2Feli-lilly-antibody-trial-is-paused-because-of-potential-safety-concerns&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2ptjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=3b8ebcb5\" data-auto-link ta